2 police officers killed, suspect dead after Innisfil, Ont. shooting
By
Gabby Rodrigues
Global News
Posted October 12, 2022 12:27 am
Updated October 13, 2022 7:29 am
2:52
2 police officers fatally shot in Innisfil, Ont.
WATCH ABOVE: Two South Simcoe Police officers and a 23-year-old suspect are dead after a shooting in Innisfil, Ont. Catherine McDonald reports from the community – Oct 12, 2022
